data.description: Awesome opportunity to grab this 4 unit, fully furnished building, for a great turn-key results.3 units are identical, with beautiful islands, to utilize seating. High end maple cabinets, with stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms fully updated with surround units. All units have their own 90% efficency units. New roof. This building is on a corner lot in a quiet area, with brand new paved parking lot, that can accomadate up to 16 parking spaces. All units are fully furnished, and all funishing are included in the sale (ask for a list) tenants are on leases. Downstairs units (x's 2) are getting $1300. Upstairs units, $1325 (x's 2 )at the moment. Great opportunity to live in one unit, and rent out the others. Listing agent to be present for all showings. Please, do not disturb other tenants. Please allow 24 hour notice to show.
